divs: Sighting DetailsI was driving home from work, down Thompson Dr. and i looked to the side just above a yellow house that used to be a daycare, and i saw a large cylindrical object, moving very low through the trees, but just above the houses, i stopped my car and watched it to the annoyance to the cars behind me. i don't know how no one else even seemed to notice it. i only told my sister and she thought i was kidding and when i told her i wasn't she seemed to think i was lying. i never told anyone else. i know what i saw and i am not saying its aliens but I know it wasn't a blimp or anything else there were trees behind it and in front it. I have no history of seeing things that are not there. I don't know what it was but i know it was something
